import Link from 'next/link'
import {Menu,Container,Image} from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default () => (
    <Menu invented fixed="top" size="huge">
        <Link href="/" prefetch passHref>
            <Image
                size="mini"
                src="/static/moltin-light-hex.svg"
                style={{marginRight:'1.5em'}}
            />
            NextJs Store
        </Link>
    </Menu>
)
